fixture.name: Match 2
fixture.resultText: Sydney Sixers Women win by 3 wickets with 6 balls remaining
fixture.tossResult: Sydney Sixers Women won the toss and elected to bowl.

balls.Commentry: FOUR! Sophie Molineux to Caoimhe Bray. Length ball, driving, Hit Hard in the air under control past deep extra cover for 4 runs. Set 179 to win the Sixers get home by 3 wickets with 6 balls to spare. An impressive batting performance from Player of the Match Ellyse Perry set the foundation for the chase. Late wickets kept the Renegades in the contest, but Sarah Bryce played a important knock to see the Sixers over the line.
